  "page": "Robert Vance",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Vance_of_Atranta\" title=\"House Vance of Atranta\"><img alt=\"House Vance of Atranta.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5d/House_Vance_of_Atranta.svg/50px-House_Vance_of_Atranta.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5d/House_Vance_of_Atranta.svg/75px-House_Vance_of_Atranta.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/5d/House_Vance_of_Atranta.svg/100px-House_Vance_of_Atranta.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Lord</span><br />Robert Vance</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Vance_of_Wayfarer%27s_Rest\" title=\"House Vance of Wayfarer&#39;s Rest\"><img alt=\"House Vance of Wayfarer&#39;s Rest.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/House_Vance_of_Wayfarer%27s_Rest.svg/50px-House_Vance_of_Wayfarer%27s_Rest.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/House_Vance_of_Wayfarer%27s_Rest.svg/75px-House_Vance_of_Wayfarer%27s_Rest.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/House_Vance_of_Wayfarer%27s_Rest.svg/100px-House_Vance_of_Wayfarer%27s_Rest.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Titles</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord\" title=\"Lord\">Lord</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/River_king\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"River king\">River king</a>/<a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Trident\" title=\"King of the Trident\">King of the Trident</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Vance\" title=\"House Vance\">House Vance</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Rivermen\" title=\"Rivermen\">Rivermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Robert Vance</b> was the head of one of the branches of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Vance\" title=\"House Vance\">House Vance</a> four centuries before the <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">Aegon's Conquest</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Robert_Vance&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Robert claimed the title of <a href=\"/index.php/River_king\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"River king\">river king</a> or <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Trident\" title=\"King of the Trident\">King of the Trident</a> in the generations after the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a> were conquered by the <a href=\"/index.php/Storm_King\" title=\"Storm King\">Storm King</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Arlan_III_Durrandon\" title=\"Arlan III Durrandon\">Arlan III Durrandon</a>. Lord Robert had a brief and inglorious reign before being put down.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Robert_Vance&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Riverlands.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403135437\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.065 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.254 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 419/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10434/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 5550/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 383/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 571/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.170/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.46 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  244.120      1 -total\n 97.59%  238.241      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 96.77%  236.243      1 Template:Infobox\n 11.84%   28.910     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  4.88%   11.913      4 Template:Infobox_label\n  1.79%    4.372      1 Template:Ref\n  1.23%    3.007      1 Template:Ref/core\n  0.55%    1.350      1 Template:References\n  0.35%    0.848      1 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaft